replies.body:
Stashu I'd like to thank you for still listening to the community and keeping on working with this champion after all the hate you got. I'm no Cassiopeia main but I can imagine how bad it could feel to work on something for months only to learn that people hate your work and you have to do it all over again. This is the kind of work attitude we don't really see anywhere, so I want to reward you with my cookie for your hard job. {{item:2052}} 
I hope in the end you can come up with something the community likes and keep on working with other champions.
Despite all the frustrations I think everyone involved in the rework learned a lot about providing and listening to feedback, so the next reworks should come much smoother.
